# AI Coach retrieval index — built locally from the RAG corpus by
# tools/question_audit/src/build_coach_index.py. It contains extracted text from
# the source documents, and our corpus rule is "grounding only, not
# redistributed" (same reason corpus/*.pdf is ignored). Firebase uploads
# everything under functions/ on deploy, so the function still receives it.
functions/coach_index.json
